mmo starting age 40:</b> Biennial screeening mammo starting age 40\n                            \n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            <b>If:</b>\n                            \n                            <i>Applicability:</i>\n                            \n                            <i>(ExistsUSPSTFAvgRisk)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            <b>Then:</b> <i>Definition:</i> <code>http://cancerscreeningcds.github.io/bcsm-cds/ActivityDefinition/BreastScreeningServiceRequest|1.0.0</code><br/>\n                            \n                            <i>Dynamic Values:</i><br/>\n                            \n                            %action.code[0].coding[0]: <i>(USPSTFAvgRiskCode)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            %action.timingTiming: <i>(USPSTFAvgRiskTiming)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            code.coding[0]: <i>(USPSTFAvgRiskCode)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            occurrenceDateTime: <i>(USPSTFAvgRiskTimingEvent)</i>\n                            <br/>\n                            \n                            \n                            \n                            \n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                </table>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        \n    </table>\n</div>\n</div>"
